Modification notice
-------------------

epics-rs is a Rust reimplementation of EPICS-related software. Except where
files are explicitly imported from upstream projects (for example bundled OPI
assets), the repository does not contain verbatim copies of the original C/C++
implementation. The Rust crates in this repository were independently written
while following the public behavior, protocols, record semantics, database
formats, and runtime architecture of the upstream projects listed below.

Where an upstream license requires notice of changes to modified or derived
copies, this file serves as that notice: specified portions were reimplemented,
adapted, reorganized, and/or translated into Rust for use in this repository.

